Package: lissyrtools
Title: Tools for LISSY Jobs
Version: 0.1.6
Authors@R: c(person("Josep", "Espasa Reig", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "jespasareig@gmail.com"))
Author: Josep Espasa Reig [aut, cre]
Description: Tools for the computation of inequality indicators in LISSY. 
  This package contains three different types of functions. 'Read', 'transformation' 
   and 'output' functions. 'Read functions' should allow LISSY users to read LIS and LWS files
  with functionalities that extend those provided by 'read.LIS()'. Transformation functions add
  easy data manipulation stages to LISSY jobs. Output functions help users create outputs and
  plots for their tasks.
License: GPL-3
